ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.points

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.points.Point
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    POIPoint, UserPoint

    public class Point
extends java.lang.Object
    Point is a class that represents a general point on earth. A point is described by three components:
    • Latitude
    • Longitude
    • Altitude

    This class contains a method to compute distance in meters between two points.
